## Deployment Steps

1. Add `OPENAI_API_KEY` to [Vercel Environment Variables](https://vercel.com/docs/environment-variables).
2. Deploy — Vercel auto-detects [api/match.js](file:///f:/Extention/Resume/api/match.js) as a serverless function.
3. Test:
   ```bash
   curl -X POST https://YOUR-URL/api/match \
     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
     -d '{"resumeText":"Python engineer with AWS experience","jobDescription":"Senior Python developer for cloud infrastructure"}'
   ```
